Definition.WordDefinition:
Pink \Pink\, n. [D. pink.] (Naut.) A vessel with a very narrow stern; -- called also {pinky}. --Sir W. Scott. [1913 Webster]
{Pink stern} (Naut.), a narrow stern. [1913 Webster]
